---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import SiteFooter from '../components/SiteFooter.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy — What's My Time Worth"
  description="What data this calculator collects (mostly nothing), how Google Analytics and AdSense are used, and how to opt out of tracking."
>
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <a href="/" class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-mute hover:text-blood">
      &larr; Back to the calculator
    </a>

    <h1 class="font-display font-light text-5xl md:text-6xl tracking-tightest mt-8 mb-6">
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>

    <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-mute mb-10">
      Last updated: April 18, 2026
    </p>

    <p class="font-display italic text-2xl text-ink-soft mb-16 leading-snug">
      A plain-language account of what this site does and does not collect.
    </p>

    <article class="prose-custom space-y-10 font-body text-lg leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-light text-3xl tracking-tightest mb-4">
          The short version
        </h2>
        <p>
          The calculator itself collects nothing. All calculations run in your
          browser. The numbers you enter are never sent to a server, stored in
          a database, or linked to you in any way.
        </p>
        <p>
          The site as a whole uses two third-party services that do collect
          anonymized data: Google Analytics for traffic measurement and
          Google AdSense for advertising. Details below.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-light text-3xl tracking-tightest mb-4">
          Who runs this site
        </h2>
        <p>
          This site is operated by an independent publisher based in Ontario,
          Canada. For questions about this policy or how data is handled, use
          the{' '}
          <a href="/contact" class="underline decoration-blood decoration-2 underline-offset-4 hover:text-blood">
            contact form
          </a>
          .
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-light text-3xl tracking-tightest mb-4">
          What the calculator collects
        </h2>
        <p>
          Nothing. Every number you enter into the wage calculator — your
          salary, state, hours, spending, age — lives in your browser's
          temporary memory only. When you close the tab, it is gone. We do
          not log, store, transmit, or analyze any of your inputs. There is
          no account system, no email capture, and no form submission that
          reaches us.
        </p>
        <p>
          The share image you generate is created in your browser using the
          HTML Canvas API. It is never uploaded anywhere. When you download
          or copy it, you are copying a file your browser made locally.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-light text-3xl tracking-tightest mb-4">
          Google Analytics
        </h2>
        <p>
          We use Google Analytics 4 to understand how people find and use
          this site. Analytics collects anonymized information such as the
          pages you visit, approximate geographic location (country and
          region, not street address), device type, browser, and how you
          arrived at the site. It does not link this information to your
          real identity.
        </p>
        <p>
          Analytics uses cookies to recognize returning visitors. If you
          prefer not to be counted, you can install Google's official{' '}
          <a
            href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="underline decoration-blood decoration-2 underline-offset-4 hover:text-blood"
          >
            Analytics opt-out browser extension
          </a>{' '}
          or use a browser that blocks tracking scripts.
        </p>
        <p>
          Google's use of this data is governed by their{' '}
          <a
            href="https://policies.google.com/privacy"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="underline decoration-blood decoration-2 underline-offset-4 hover:text-blood"
          >
            privacy policy
          </a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-light text-3xl tracking-tightest mb-4">
          Google AdSense
        </h2>
        <p>
          This site is supported by advertising served by Google AdSense.
          Google and its partners use cookies and similar technologies to
          show ads that may be personalized based on your browsing history
          across the web.
        </p>
        <p>
          Specifically:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc pl-6">
          <li>
            Third-party vendors, including Google, use cookies to serve ads
            based on your prior visits to this site and other sites on the
            web.
          </li>
          <li>
            Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners
            to serve ads based on your visits to this site and other sites on
            the internet.
          </li>
          <li>
            You can opt out of personalized advertising by visiting{' '}
            <a
              href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="underline decoration-blood decoration-2 underline-offset-4 hover:text-blood"
            >
              Google Ads Settings
            </a>
            .
          </li>
          <li>
            You can also opt out of a third-party vendor's use of cookies for
            personalized advertising by visiting{' '}
            <a
              href="https://www.aboutads.info/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="underline decoration-blood decoration-2 underline-offset-4 hover:text-blood"
            >
              aboutads.info
            </a>
            .
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-light text-3xl tracking-tightest mb-4">
          Cookies
        </h2>
        <p>
          The site uses cookies only through the third-party services named
          above (Google Analytics and Google AdSense). We do not set our own
          cookies. You can disable cookies in your browser settings at any
          time; the calculator will continue to function normally.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-light text-3xl tracking-tightest mb-4">
          Your rights under privacy law
        </h2>
        <p>
          Depending on where you live, you may have legal rights regarding
          data about you. Because the calculator itself does not collect or
          store any personal information, most of these rights are effectively
          already honored. For data collected by Google Analytics and
          AdSense, those rights are exercised through Google directly using
          the opt-out links provided in this policy.
        </p>

        <h3 class="font-display text-xl mt-6 mb-2">If you are in Canada (PIPEDA)</h3>
        <p class="text-base">
          Under the Personal Information Protection and Electronic Documents
          Act, you have the right to know what personal information is held
          about you and to correct it. We hold no personal information about
          you directly. For information held by Google, contact Google.
        </p>

        <h3 class="font-display text-xl mt-6 mb-2">If you are in California (CCPA / CPRA)</h3>
        <p class="text-base">
          You have the right to know what personal information has been
          collected, the right to delete it, the right to opt out of its
          sale or sharing, and the right to non-discrimination. We do not
          sell your information. For opt-out of personalized advertising,
          use the Google Ads Settings link above.
        </p>

        <h3 class="font-display text-xl mt-6 mb-2">If you are in the EU or UK (GDPR / UK GDPR)</h3>
        <p class="text-base">
          You have the right to access, correct, or delete data about you,
          and to object to processing. Because we do not collect personal
          data directly, most requests should be directed to Google in its
          capacity as data processor. The legal basis for processing via
          Google Analytics and AdSense is legitimate interest or, where
          required, consent expressed through your continued use of the
          site and your browser's cookie settings.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-light text-3xl tracking-tightest mb-4">
          Children
        </h2>
        <p>
          This site is not directed at children under 13, and we do not
          knowingly collect any data from them. If you are under 13, you
          should not use this site.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-light text-3xl tracking-tightest mb-4">
          Changes to this policy
        </h2>
        <p>
          We may update this policy as the site evolves or as laws change.
          The "last updated" date at the top of this page will reflect the
          most recent revision. Material changes will be reflected in the
          date. If the changes are significant, we will highlight them
          visibly on the site for a period of time.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-light text-3xl tracking-tightest mb-4">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about this policy or the data practices described here go
          through the{' '}
          <a href="/contact" class="underline decoration-blood decoration-2 underline-offset-4 hover:text-blood">
            contact form
          </a>
          .
        </p>
      </section>
    </article>

    <footer class="mt-24 pt-12 border-t border-ink/10">
      <a href="/" class="btn-primary">Back to the calculator</a>
    </footer>
  </main>

  <SiteFooter />
</Base>

<style is:global>
  .prose-custom h2 { margin-top: 2rem; }
  .prose-custom h3 { margin-top: 1.5rem; }
  .prose-custom strong { font-weight: 600; color: #1A1A1A; }
  .prose-custom em { font-style: italic; }
  .prose-custom ul { margin: 1rem 0; }
  .prose-custom li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
</style>
